# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

A bulk sync replicates entire tables or objects from a source connection to a destination connection. Unlike [model syncs](../resources/sync), which operate on individual field mappings, bulk syncs transfer complete schemas with minimal configuration.

For connection-specific configuration details, see the [Polytomic connection guides](https://apidocs.polytomic.com/guides/configuring-your-connections).

